				%strong Project Description
			%p	This is my personal website, built using Ruby on Rails (you are here).

			%h3
				%strong How It Works
			%p This uses Ruby v4 with haml and the other usual suspects. It includes a portfolio section with individual pages for each project, resume page, and blog. I've included a modal, and an expandable navbar that works with the Rails views. I have open sourced the code.

			%h3
				%strong Contribution
			%p Solo. Designed, developed, deployed, including personal url setup and all art and photos. It's all me, friends. Started with a template that I ended up mostly redoing.

			%h3
				%strong Project Details
			%ul
