					Ruby on Rails
				%li
					%strong Front End:
					HTML, CSS, Javascript, JQuery
				%li
					%strong Templating and Presentation:
					Haml, Bootstrap
				%li
					%strong Testing:
					RSpec, Capybara, FactoryGirl, Better Errors, Byebug
				%li
					%strong Tools and Misc:
					Markdown for the blog posts, Google Analytics, Pundit, SendGrid, FriendlyID, Simple Form, Devise
				%li
					%strong Cloud Infrastructure and DevOps:
					Heroku
				%li
					%strong DB:
					SQLite (development), PostgreSQL (production)
				-#%li
